{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSToolBarTop","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"code":"toolBarTop(_:hasLargeTitle:subtitle:leadingItems:trailingItems:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"  View helper applies a SwiftUI toolbar configuration.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Appearances","anchor":"Appearances","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"With Liquid Glass \/ iOS 26+ the OS will change the rendering of the toolbar items depending to the context:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The OS can group the items of same types in one group with kind of rectangle (e.g. views with menus)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"But for buttons items they will remain isolated"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The placement of the title can be leading or centered depending to the length of the text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The text can be truncated if there is not enough remaining space"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The OS can apply another style for the back button"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Without Liquid Glass \/ iOS 18 and lower, the OS won’t change that much the style of the toolbar items, Items won’t be visually grouped.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Globaly the appearence of the * navigation bar* elements is changed by the ","type":"text"},{"code":"oudsNavigationBarAppearance","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"helper of ","type":"text"},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" that must be applyed on the root view of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"NavigationStack","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" for example.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Technical constraints","anchor":"Technical-constraints","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To be sure for iOS 18 and lower the back buttton and text have the good color, in your main view apply the following accent color:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    struct AppMainView: View {","        var body: some View {","            ContentView()","                .accentColor(theme.colors.contentDefault)","        }","    }"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Platform considerations","anchor":"Platform-considerations","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component is available on iOS, iPadOS, and visionOS"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component is not available for watchOS, tvOS and macOS"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Code sample","anchor":"Code-sample","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"code":["    ContentView()","        .toolBarTop(\"Title\",","            leadingItems: {","                OUDSToolBarItem(navigation: .back())","            },","            trailingItems: {","                OUDSToolBarItem(label: \"Label\") { \/* Action to process *\/ }","                OUDSToolBarItem(icon: Image(decorative: \"some_image\"), accessibilityLabel: \"Label\") { \/* Action to process *\/ }","            }","        )"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-ios-tool-